00:20:08.539 --> 00:20:10.539
Clark, just...

00:20:10.539 --> 00:20:12.539
You can't think that way.

00:20:16.539 --> 00:20:17.539
Just...

00:20:17.539 --> 00:20:19.539
You know, I remember the first time I met her.

00:20:19.539 --> 00:20:20.539
It was eighth grade.

00:20:20.539 --> 00:20:22.539
I was like, it's so funny.

00:20:22.539 --> 00:20:23.539
I thought she was crazy.

00:20:23.539 --> 00:20:25.539
I was like, I'm just going to fuck her.

00:20:25.539 --> 00:20:26.539
She's just so perfect.

00:20:26.539 --> 00:20:27.940
It was eighth grade.

00:20:29.379 --> 00:20:31.200
